Considering that the population sequencing data may come from different platforms, the RD of each individual sample was counted and corrected. Because the resequencing samples may show various GC content distributions, the GC bias was corrected individually, similar to the method used in CNVnator (CNVnator, RRID:SCR_010821) [23]:
